snippet.title: Tamagotchi Connection V5 Familitchi
snippet.description: More family equals more fun with the new Tamagotchi Familitchi from Bandai America!  As the most technologically advanced version of the world's first and top selling "virtual pet" tech toy, the V5 allows kids to experience fun family values while raising multiple characters simultaneously in one egg. Based on how they are raised, they can grow up as an intellectual, artistic, cheerful or even a laid back family.  V5 also extends its magical virtual world with the new Tama & Earth Expo at TamaTown.com.
